dcterms:description: The Electricity Transformer Temperature (ETT) dataset measures the long-term deployment of electric power, consisting of two hourly-sampled datasets (ETTh) and two 15-minute-sampled datasets (ETTm) collected over 2 years from two different Chinese provinces.
